_sText:
Revision analysis:

-Improved Frames-per-second (in most areas)

-Cleaner textures (all default, no pakrat needed)

-Fixed prop_physics (no more low gravity bouncing vending machines etc... ^^)

-Improved spawns and team balance (no more cheap spots)

-Better lighting (no hdr) 1up for fps

-Crisp environment and optimization (no more bitching)

I tried to keep the map as original as possible. Poon (original author) gave me permission modify and release this map. 

I did minor adjustments for balance purposes. 

Credit goes to Poon (much appreciated :)
